      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DEEP SPACE (2) boasts a consistent overall record including four wins from 20 starts, but missed the frame latest when fourth (30.48) over 520m at this track. Super consistent and looks a key player. ZIPPING BILPIN (8) was a winner two back when prominent throughout then got further back last time and could manage only a 3.5 lengths 3rd at Wentworth Park (30.14). The form out of his last race has been franked. Bold showing expected. RONALDO VELLA (5) had been in great form, scoring back to wins before copping a check last time and finishing sixth (30.15), beaten 7 lengths in a Grade 5 at Wentworth Park. Has good speed and will be prominent despite the squeeze draw. Rates a leading chance. SPIN AROUND BLUE (1) comes into calculations after placing in a quick run most recently.",
